snippet.title: Official Launch Trailer - Captain ToonHead vs The Punks from Outer Space
snippet.description:
Captain ToonHead is available now! Experience tower defense from the front lines and become the hero we got stuck with in this narrative-driven and cartoony adventure. Master and upgrade a ridiculous arsenal of blasters, the mighty chancla, and gnarly towers to defeat Nicholas Voorhees' Punk Army and save Earth!
-------

Lyrics:
Elliott was a janitor
Nobody cared for him
He went on a mission 
with the Bestest Squad team

Oh my ! they did not put that burrito in the microwave!
Now he’s the hero we got stuck with
He’s Captain ToonHead

Fighting Voorhees
and his Punk Army
Captain ToonHead
